## 🃏 New Card Reference

---

### 🍄 Magic Mushroom — Info
**Look at the top 5 cards of the deck.** You may take one of the cards and replace it with one of the cards from your hand and place them on the deck in any order.


*"I see… brown. Lots of brown. And something awful."*

---

### 🎰 Roll Rewind — Dice Modifier / Reaction
**Discard a card to reroll any single die result** — yours or another player's — immediately after it's rolled. Play as a reaction.

*"I prefer my odds pre-loaded."*

---

### 🔄 Cookie Swap — Social
**Swap your entire hand with any other player's hand.** A Shield Spell can be played in reaction to cancel this effect.

*"Surprise! Their hand was worse."*

---

### 🧙 Dungeon Master — Dice / Attack
**Declare a number 1–6.** Force any player to roll the die.

- If they **miss***: they discard 1 card.
- If they roll your **declared number exactly**: nothing happens.

*"I am the architect of your suffering."*

---

### 🍪 Jar Bait — Cookie Jar Roll
**Play on any other player** That player must immediately **Tempt the Jar** — rolling the die and resolving the Cookie Jar Roll effect.
This ends your turn. Game resumes from the player who should have followed you.

> ⚠️ The discard pile minimum of **1 Milk Splashes** still applies. If the pile is too small, this card is wasted.

*"The jar called. It's personal."*

